                     <interp inst="t17450911-16-person164" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the Prisoner ever since she was born.</p>
               <p>Q. Is not she a relation of yours?</p>
               <p>Crisp. Yes, she is a relation of mine. She came of a very honest family, and I believe no body can stain the family with any thing but this - I am her sister. <rs id="t17450911-16-verdict81" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17450911-16-verdict81" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
